longBusinessSummary: Digital Utilities Ventures, Inc., through its wholly owned subsidiary, Torq Communications, Inc., provides real time video transport system for the Internet. It offers The New Last Mile, a first live Internet to TV/cell phone broadcasting system. The company is headquartered in Fort Lauderdale, Florida.
